instructions:
Use the terminal (cli) command to get png file of figma designs and then read it via gemini_ai_chat_with_files: dmtools figma_download_image_of_file <<EOF
{
  "href": "https://www.figma.com/design/asdsadasdasdasd/Business-App?m=auto&node-id=NODEID&t=ASdasdsadas-1"
}
EOF

**IMPORTANT** You must check child tickets via following command to get better context like questions answers, solution designs, etc. Use the terminal (cli) command to get existing questions in the ticket: dmtools jira_search_by_jql <<EOF
{
  "jql": "parent = TICKET-XXX"
}
EOF
